title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 12 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 12 2022
description:
Ask every doctor who treats you if they think Fauci did a good job. CDC suddenly drops everything on covid in newest guidance. What Pocahontas says she needs to be president. WSJ publishes list of items the FBI seized from Mar-a-Lago. Julie Kelly joins Clay to discuss the Mar-a-Lago raid and the Gretchen Whitmer case. Can Novak Djokovic play in the U.S. Open now that the CDC admits there's no difference between vaccinated and unvaccinated people? Should he just go enter the U.S. through the southern border and take a bus to New York?

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
